platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Convinced youve run out of things to watch? Amazon Prime Video may be able to prove otherwise. The app is brimming with brilliant films, dramas, and comedies, as well as sports and childrens TV, all available to watch on demand. We love the ultra-high-quality 4K streaming and the slick UI. Oh, and the ability to create multiple user profiles and download series to watch later. There are also hundreds of Amazon Originals to check outgreat series and films produced by Amazon Studios that you wont find anywhere else.
